title: Jackson vs Oasis (Mashup Album) (Jackson 5 v.s Oasis)
description:
The following bootleg album is done using mixes between Oasis and Jackson 5 (with some early Michael stuff thrown in for measure). Extra production was used to help fuse the two together but no work by any other artist was used in this mix.

The mix comprises of the following tracks:

1 I want your Wonderwall (oasis v.s jackson 5) 3:54
2 Feel With It (oasis v.s jackson 5) 2:02 
3 Don't Rock 'Til You Get Enough (part 1) (oasis v.s Jackson 5) 2:37 
4 Don't Rock 'Til You Get Enough (part 2) (oasis v.s Jackson 5) 3:19 
5 Eternal Light (BigBadBaz Remix) 4:40 
6 Stand By Your Alphabet (oasis v.s jackson 5) 5:08 0
7 The Love You Save (oasis v.s jackson 5) 3:16 
8 Ben'Ding Time (Oasis v.s Jackson 5) 3:23 
9 Goodbye World (oasis v.s jackson 5) 3:06
